{"tid":2517735,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金融時報：對駐港跨國企業的高層而言，最大威脅是香港有傳媒自由，而非香港人權遭削弱","createTime":"2021-05-05T13:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T13:39:32.000Z","uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a8873560aefb29ee29a6d3402ecf33da8da3d9e3","tid":2517735,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"英國金融時報的亞洲新聞編輯 Anderlini 發表評論，批評一些負責中國業務的國際公司高管患了「斯德哥爾摩症候群」，明明面對中國政府諸多刁難，但依然把問題歸咎其他人，而非造成這些問題的中國政府。<br />\n<br />\n他說，近日跟一班駐港跨國企業的高層交流，一些來自民主國家的管理層說，對他們而言，最大威脅是香港有傳媒自由，而非香港人權遭削弱，因為駐港記者如實報導香港情況，可能令公司總部由香港撤資。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.ft.com/content/51e1a437-3aca-42ed-8403-2a05b338622b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F51e1a437-3aca-42ed-8403-2a05b338622b&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn67XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=bf680257\" target=\"_blank\">https://amp.ft.com/content/51e1a437-3aca-42ed-8403-2a05b338622b</a>"},{"pid":"8eada658d799d92df2e2144278fa0fd24164951b","tid":2517735,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/europechinese/photos/a.566872090026410/3926748230705429/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Feuropechinese%2Fphotos%2Fa.566872090026410%2F3926748230705429%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn67XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=53eb23f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/europechinese/photos/a.566872090026410/3926748230705429/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"928bc018f710e1d931cb7e38b12d0ccb276f60b7","tid":2517735,"uid":19527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"Companies like Volkswagen, Apple, Starbucks, Nike, Intel, Qualcomm, General Motors and H&amp;M are all reliant on the huge and growing Chinese market. Various western companies, including several of these, have lobbied in public or in private on behalf of the same government that 